WEBVTT

00:03:29.486 --> 00:03:33.670
I get to read about mother-in-law
jokes from Mesopotamia

00:03:33.694 --> 00:03:35.246
from 3,500 years ago.

00:03:35.270 --> 00:03:36.801
(Laughter)

00:03:37.975 --> 00:03:41.379
I get to hear about neighbors
cursing each other

00:03:41.403 --> 00:03:43.901
from 4,600 years ago in Egypt.

00:03:43.925 --> 00:03:48.528
And my absolute favorite,
from 3,300 years ago in Luxor:

00:03:48.552 --> 00:03:54.060
an inscription that describes schoolboys
who cut class to go drinking.

00:03:54.084 --> 00:03:56.054
(Laughter)

00:03:56.078 --> 00:03:58.046
Kids these days.

00:03:58.070 --> 00:03:59.394
(Laughter)

00:03:59.882 --> 00:04:03.242
I get to see the most
incredible architecture,